data.description: OPEN HOUSE on Sunday September 24th from 2pm to 4pm!  Charming home in the heart of Southside, less than a mile from IH-35. In a quiet, established neighborhood, with mature trees in the front and back yard. This classic floorplan has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a bonus big room that could be use as a 4th bedroom/office/game room. Updated with laminate floors. No carpet! Book your showing today!
